{"tid":2368272,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★許樹昌：沒有禁足令 市民仍然可以上班、病毒一樣可以散開去","createTime":"2021-01-16T05:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T06:07:02.000Z","uid":19454,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e792166c7fb8dc107be6057fb11929e927ff0c46","tid":2368272,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:06:21.000Z","msg":"許樹昌：「技術上有這困難，因為裡面舊樓有很多劏房沒有住客名單，很難追蹤到有沒有走了。內地一有小區爆發，即刻有禁足令，接著做檢測，沒有禁足令，市民仍然<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>可以上班</strong></span>、去食肆、商場，病毒一樣可以散開去，但香港來說，市民對這方面的抗拒可能很大。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=420511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D420511&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyC3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=f2447bc4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D420511&h=08d4e399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=420511</a>"},{"pid":"bbcf8507a5befb0c465ae658e89599de1ed0dd14","tid":2368272,"uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:06:53.000Z","msg":"黎生jpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a501b7b9c9f10924e83904e73ee24bdff668fdd","tid":2368272,"uid":242537,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"bbcf8507a5befb0c465ae658e89599de1ed0dd14","tid":2368272,"uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:06:53.000Z","msg":"黎生jpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy"